- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper focuses on the use of machine learning techniques for IDS. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper discusses classical AI techniques for IDS. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is a possible category as IDS are used to monitor computer networks. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper discusses the development of software for IDS.
